      "file": "CLAUDE.md",
      "line": 1
    },
    {
      "title": "monitor_dashboard.py — 修复硬编码路径",
      "description": "将 DATA_PATH 和 LOG_PATH 从 /root/projects/量子电路/... 改为基于 os.path.abspath(__file__) 的相对路径，确保跨环境可移植性。",
      "file": "monitor_dashboard.py",
      "line": 9
    },
    {
      "title": "cleanup_and_setup.sh — 参数化 PROJECT_ROOT",
      "description": "将所有 /root/quantum 硬编码替换为 $PROJECT_ROOT 变量，支持通过第一个参数传入项目路径，默认为当前目录。",
      "file": "cleanup_and_setup.sh",
      "line": 8
    },
    {
      "title": "run_train_v13.sh — 移除 SSH 敏感信息",
      "description": "将注释中的 AutoDL 服务器 IP (connect.westd.seetacloud.com) 和端口 (14191) 替换为文档引用，避免敏感信息进入版本控制。",
      "file": "run_train_v13.sh",
      "line": 7
    },
    {
      "title": "configs/ — 超参数配置目录",
      "description": "新建 configs/ 目录，将 V9/V13 训练超参数提取为独立 yaml 文件：v9_baseline.yaml、v9_fallback.yaml、v13_gpu.yaml。",
      "file": "configs/v13_gpu.yaml",
      "line": 1
    },
    {
      "title": "train.py — 统一训练入口",
      "description": "新建统一训练入口，通过 --config 参数加载 yaml 配置，取代各脚本中的硬编码参数。用法：python train.py --config configs/v9_baseline.yaml",
      "file": "train.py",
      "line": 1
    },
    {
      "title": "notebooks/ — 规范化的 Notebook 目录",
